commit 7755f2438ff239770c322af09371cabdfba4bbbe
Author: Bruce Hill <bhill@slac.stanford.edu>
Date:   Thu Nov 16 00:32:28 2017 -0800

    Add custom rules for autosave, archive, alh, and Restore files.
    
    Also allows building db and other generated files from ioc directories.
    
    Also made sure *.cmd and *.proto files can be installed via CMD += and PROTO +=.
    Default INSTALL dir for both is INSTALL_LOCATION/db, but that can be overridden
    by redefining INSTALL_CMD and INSTALL_PROTO.
    
    Build fix for templated IOC archive and request files

